cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper discusses the performance of deep artificial neural networks in image classification tasks, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also touches on the topic of expressivity of neural networks, which falls under the sub-category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves extensive experiments and data analysis, which could also be relevant to the sub-category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
